name: git
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "2.18.0" %}

package:
  name: git
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/git/git/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz  # [not win]
  sha256: 93993babac690a06906d832a1715c3315b4787a2845aeb500f7dcc82e1599df2  # [not win]
  patches:                                              # [not win]
    - 0001-macOS-Do-not-use-the-system-Wish-urgh.patch  # [not win]

  url: https://github.com/git-for-windows/git/releases/download/v{{ version }}.windows.1/PortableGit-{{ version }}-64-bit.7z.exe  # [win64]
  sha256: cd84a13b6c7aac0e924cb4db2476e2f4379aab4b8e60246992a6c5eebeac360c  # [win64]

build:
  number: 1
  # git hardcodes paths to external utilities (e.g. curl)
  detect_binary_files_with_prefix: true
  # we don't actually build on windows, don't need multiple VC builds
  skip: true  # [win and vc!=14]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}  # [unix]
    - autoconf  # [unix]
    - make      # [unix]
    - 7za       # [win]
  host:
    - curl      # [unix]
    - expat     # [unix]
    - gettext   # [unix]
    - libiconv  # [unix]
    - openssl   # [unix]
    - perl      # [unix]
    - tk        # [unix]
    - zlib      # [unix]
  run:
    - curl      # [unix]
    - expat     # [unix]
    - gettext   # [unix]
    - libiconv  # [unix]
    - openssl   # [unix]
    - perl      # [unix]
    - tk        # [unix]
    - zlib      # [unix]

test:
  commands:
    # Verify git location.
    - test -f $PREFIX/bin/git                               # [unix]
    - test -f $PREFIX/bin/gitk                              # [unix]
    - if not exist %LIBRARY_PREFIX%\\bin\\git.exe exit 1    # [win]

    # Verify interactive support.
    - test -f $PREFIX/libexec/git-core/git-add--interactive  # [unix]

    # Run git commands.
    - git --version
    - git clone https://github.com/conda-forge/git-feedstock

    # test completions
    - bash $PREFIX/share/bash-completion/completions/git  # [unix]
    - conda inspect linkages -p $PREFIX $PKG_NAME  # [not win]
    - conda inspect objects -p $PREFIX $PKG_NAME  # [osx]

about:
  home: https://git-scm.com/
  license: GPL v2 and LGPL 2.1
  license_file: COPYING  # [not win]
  summary: distributed version control system

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - msarahan
    - pelson
    - scopatz
    - ocefpaf
    - dougalsutherland
